{"tid":2224201,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"反黑警疑炮製假掃賭 事前邀黑幫入警署傾安排戲子被捕","createTime":"2020-09-30T10:45:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T12:37:23.000Z","uid":240362,"like":69,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"e39e7b077d3e66b0ed45fefcbf314d919ee4d3b1","tid":2224201,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:45:55.000Z","msg":"反黑警員疑設局造假，串同黑幫成員策劃「掃蕩」非法賭場，但只會拘捕假賭客並撿取少量賭具及賭款。涉案賭場負責人今在區域法院承認串謀妨礙司法公正罪，案情披露疑有反黑警在掃賭行動前，警署會對黑幫成員中門大開，反黑警疑帶領黑幫成員手下進入警署開會，向對方建議事前如何佈置賭場及揀選戲子賭客。詎料，該手下原來是反黑委派滲入黑幫的臥底。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200930/BJWFUDCZLNHFNACMJXMFWCHG2M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200930%2FBJWFUDCZLNHFNACMJXMFWCHG2M%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kygbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=76bcc545\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200930%2FBJWFUDCZLNHFNACMJXMFWCHG2M%2F&h=5b273787\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200930/BJWFUDCZLNHFNACMJXMFWCHG2M/</a>"},{"pid":"6dab1c5e7be6d296d2993039f4e10a1dcbf045d9","tid":2224201,"uid":305767,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冚賭檔，不如入去一齊睹"},{"pid":"313b09c6b0ef385ca8592091b061cca59f0b65df","tid":2224201,"uid":5195,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:48:32.000Z","msg":"反黑警疑帶領黑幫成員手下進入警署開會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8733d894fb248b8796c9ebbe9a08c1c761cac80","tid":2224201,"uid":54125,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:50:31.